  <title>Algorithms for Addition and Subtraction</title>


  <exercise workspace="10%">
    <statement>
      <p>
        Carry out the steps of the usual addition algorithm in the problems below in base 5.  Carefully EXPLAIN what each of the <q>carried</q> (regrouped or traded in) numbers mean.  You may want to refer to base 5 blocks in your explanation.
      </p>
      <p>
        <me>43_{5}+12_{5} \text{ and } 243_{5}+324_{5}</me>
      </p>
    </statement>
  </exercise>

<pagebreak />

